&lt;h1&gt;The Walton Centre NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;br /&gt;Cheshire and Merseyside Rehabilitation Network&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Therapy Services&lt;br /&gt; Physiotherapist&lt;br /&gt;Band 7&lt;br /&gt;Complex Specialist Community Service,&lt;br /&gt;St Helens and Knowsley (Locality 1)&lt;br /&gt;Garswood Health Centre, Wigan&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;22.5 hours, Part Time&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Walton Centre is the UK’s only standalone neurosciences NHS Trust, delivering a range of specialist services across a regional patch. &lt;br /&gt;The Cheshire and Merseyside Rehabilitation Network is hosted by the Walton Centre and provides complex rehabilitation services along a pathway supporting Early In –Patient through to Community based care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We need a suitably experienced Senior Physiotherapist with a strong interest in rehabilitation and community working to join our Specialist Community service. The team serves St Helens and Knowsley populations and is based at Garswood Health Centre, Wigan.&lt;br /&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;A high level of knowledge in the management of patients with diverse range of neurological conditions and multi-pathologies, experience of liaison across various health care teams and experience of working autonomously are essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will have excellent leadership and organisational skills, be an effective team player, have a flexible approach to service development / delivery and able to contribute to the strategic development and future of the service. You will have an interest in audit and research with a commitment to CPD. Your clinical and professional development will be supported by the Clinical Specialist Physiotherapist through regular appraisals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A UK driving license and access to a car during working hours are essential.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Walton Centre Therapy service offers excellent development opportunities for ambitious physiotherapists who strive for professional excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further information or to organise an informal visit please contact Mrs Emily Low, Clinical Specialist Physiotherapist 0151 556 3204 / emily.low@thewaltoncentre.nhs.uk or Ms Helen Pye, 01744 457337 / Helen.Pye1@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
